description: Some EU states could begin rolling out the Pfizer-BioNTech coronavirus vaccine as early as Sunday.
title: Covid: Pfizer-BioNTech vaccine approved for EU states
title_page: Covid: Pfizer-BioNTech vaccine approved for EU states - BBC News
maintext: Most of the side effects are very mild, similar to those after any other vaccine and usually last for a day or so, said Prof Sir Munir Pirmohamed, chairman of the UK's Commission on Human Medicine expert working group, in an interview earlier this month.
